title: Sainte-Brigitte-de-Laval
text:
Sainte-Brigitte-de-Laval is a <a href="city%20%28Quebec%29">city</a> in <a href="La%20Jacques-Cartier%20Regional%20County%20Municipality">La Jacques-Cartier Regional County Municipality</a> in the <a href="Capitale-Nationale">Capitale-Nationale</a> region of Quebec, Canada, located along the <a href="Montmorency%20River">Montmorency River</a>.
